validateObservedMetaDataFile()

Check the consistency between observed data and its dictionary. Units for `dv `and `time` need to be defined at least once in either the observed dataset, its dictionary or outputs In case of multiple definitions, warnings will thrown and the following priorities will be applied: 1. Use units from outputs 2. Use units from observed dataset 3. Use units from dictionary
